SUMMARY:Houston Grand Opera- Storybook Opera
DTSTAMP:20260701T101448Z
DTSTART:20260711T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Storytelling like you’ve never heard it before takes center sta
	ge as an opera singer presents an engaging and enjoyable introduction to o
	pera for students. This program features singing storytellers for 30 minut
	es of captivating fun! \n4/4 – Lula the Mighty Griot \n5/2 – Eyes That Mee
	t at the Corner \n6/6 – Goldilocks and the 3 Bears \n7/11 – World Cup Wome
	n \n9/5 – TBD \n10/3 – TBD \n11/7 –  TBD \n12/5 – TBD \n \n\nhttps://www.l
	evyparkhouston.org/events/houston-grand-opera-storybook-opera/2026-07-11/\
	n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/houston-grand-opera-storybook-op
	era/2026-07-11/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
