SUMMARY:Dance and Move with Young Audiences of Houston
DTSTAMP:20260701T101448Z
DTSTART:20260711T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Participants will learn to combine elements in dance\, music\, 
	and theatre while expressing themselves through creative movement. We will
	 use the fundamentals of dance to focus on story-telling while building sk
	ills in self-awareness\, social awareness\, relationship skills\, and resp
	onsible decision making.\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/1907-2/
	2026-07-11/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/1907-2/2026-07-11/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
